_sText:
Hello d00ds!,

This is a new map by me but it was based on Nippers "Falling" map from CS 1.6.

Basically you buy your guns, shoot the floor then you are off, fallling continuously while shooting the opposing team. There is a water ledge you can land on that has a few sniper rifles for campers =).

But be careful were you fall, if you miss the wooden platform at the bottom your dead!

Email: hidden_dragon1337@hotmail.com

By HiddenDragon
